T10TD4161E:166b-1: d'a na pa ri ka th'a /
T10TD4161E:166b-4: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal lo //
T10TD4161E:166b-5: sbyin pa gter chen phyi bzhin 'brangs pa yin te chom rkun la sogs dbrog mi nus //
T10TD4161E:166b-6: sbyin pa sems kyi ser sna dang ni chags pa'i skyon gyi rdul rnams 'khru bar byed //
T10TD4161E:166b-7: sbyin pa 'khor ba'i lam dang ngal bsel ba yin te bzhon pa bde blag can //
T10TD4161E:166b-8: sbyin pa bde dgur sbyor ba du ma dag gi sgo bzang gtan gyi mdza' bo mchog /'byor cing dag pa phun sum tshogs dang kun du bka' nyan yon tan rnams dang ni //
T10TD4161E:166b-9: sum cu rtsa gsum lha yul grong khyer la gnas byad gzugs mdzes pa'i yon tan rnams //
T10TD4161E:167a-1: ci 'dod de dag thams cad sbyin pa dag gis nges par thob 'gyur te //
T10TD4161E:167a-2: de ltar don ni yongs su brtags par gyur nas su dag sbyin pa sbyin mi byed //
T10TD4161E:167a-3: sbyin pa me dang chu dang chom rkun 'jigs pa'i 'khrug pa rnams kyis bskyod mi nus //
T10TD4161E:167a-4: sbyin pa sgrib pa zad byed srid pa'i 'gro ba phyi bzhin 'brang ba'i mdza' chen yin //
T10TD4161E:167a-5: sbyin pa 'gro ba'i rgyun gyi yul rnams kun du srog chags rnams kyi 'jug pa yin //
T10TD4161E:167a-6: sbyin pa tshe rabs bgrang ba dag tu phyi bzhin 'brangs te ba phyir be'u 'brang ba bzhin //
T10TD4161E:167a-7: nor rnams kun gyi snying po blang ba dbang phyug rnams kyi gzhi ni sbyin pa yin zhe'o //
T10TD4161E:167a-8: blo can legs par 'dod pa yis //
T10TD4161E:167a-9: legs par bsgrims te sbyin pa sbyin //
T10TD4161E:167a-11: sbyin pa ma gtogs gnyen med do //
T10TD4161E:167a-12: sbyin pa 'jig rten rgyan yin te //
T10TD4161E:167a-13: sbyin pa ngan 'gro zlog pa yin //
T10TD4161E:167a-14: sbyin pa mtho ris skas yin te //
T10TD4161E:167a-15: sbyin pa zhi byed shis pa yin //
T10TD4161E:167a-16: 'jig rten dag na rgyal po'i mchog / dpa' brtul dregs shing mthu che la //
T10TD4161E:167a-17: rgyal srid rgyas la dbang byed pa //
T10TD4161E:167a-18: bde 'gyung sbyin pa byin las byung //
T10TD4161E:167a-19: sum cu rtsa gsum gnas rnams na //
T10TD4161E:167a-20: brgya byin lha yi dbang byed pa //
T10TD4161E:167a-21: de yang phyin pa'i 'bras bu mchog / dam pa yin zhes mkhas rnams smra //
T10TD4161E:167a-22: mtshan mchog sum cu gnyis mda' ba //
T10TD4161E:167a-23: dri med gzi brjid mtshungs med pa //
T10TD4161E:167a-24: 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho rgal ba yang //
T10TD4161E:167a-25: sbyin pa la ni brten te 'byung //
T10TD4161E:167a-26: lha yi 'jig rten skas kyang yin //
T10TD4161E:167a-27: thar pa'i mthar gyi sgo yang yin //
T10TD4161E:167a-28: ngan song rnams las bzlog pa yin //
T10TD4161E:167a-29: phun sum tshogs kun rgyu yang yin //
T10TD4161E:167a-30: de yi phyir na mi rnams kyis //
T10TD4161E:167a-31: legs par bsgrims te sbyin pa sbyin //
T10TD4161E:167a-32: chags dang phrag dog la sogs pa //
T10TD4161E:167a-33: med par bsod nams bsags par gyis //
T10TD4161E:167a-34: sangs rgyas 'dra ba'i ston pa med //
T10TD4161E:167a-35: chos dang 'dra ba'i skyob pa med //
T10TD4161E:167a-37: de'i phyir gsum la dbul bar gyis //
T10TD4161E:167a-38: phrad par gyur pa'i mtha' ni 'bral bar 'gyur //
T10TD4161E:167a-39: phun sum tshogs pa'i mtha' ni ngan cing rgud //
T10TD4161E:167a-40: tshe 'di glog ltar 'gyur zhing 'jig la g-yo //
T10TD4161E:167a-41: de yi phyir na bag yod brtan por gyis //
T10TD4161E:167b-0: @167b 'jig rten 'di kun bde ba mngon par 'dod //
T10TD4161E:167b-1: skyes bu bde la longs spyod med par min //
T10TD4161E:167b-2: longs spyod sbyin las byung bar mkhyen nas ni //
T10TD4161E:167b-3: thub pas dang por sbyin pa'i gtam dag mdzad //
T10TD4161E:167b-4: slob dpon klu sgrub kyis mdzad pa sbyin pa'i gtam rdzogs so /
